Basic knowledge about systems modelling, such as SysML, is recommendable
Basic knowledge about object-oriented software modeling, such as UML, is recommendable
Basic skills of implementing electronic prototypes based on COTS hardware and data interfaces
General knowledge about databases is recommendable"""@es .

